MOST IMMEDIATE
No.1/34/1/2013-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 21st March, 2013
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 20th March, 2013:
(i)
Shri M.K. Alagiri relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of Chemicals and
Fertilizers;
Shri S.S. Palanimanickam relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of State
(ii)
in the Ministry of Finance;
(iii) Shri D. Napoleon relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of State in the
Ministry of Social Justice and Empowerment;
(iv) Dr. S. Jagathrakshakan relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of State in
the Ministry of Commerce and Industry;
(v)
Shri S. Gandhiselvan relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of State in the
Ministry of Health and Family Welfare; and
(vi) Shri Srikant Jena relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of State in the
Ministry of Chemicals and Fertilizers and assumed the charge of the office of the
Minister of State (Independent Charge) of the Ministry of Chemicals and Fertilizers. He
will continue to hold the charge of the office of the Minister of State (Independent
Charge) of the Ministry of Statistics and Programme Implementation.
(K.L. Sharma)
for Cabinet Secretary
Tele : 2301 5802
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded for information to the Deputy Chairman and Members of the Planning
Commission.
(K.L. Shárma)
for Cabinet Secretary
Copy forwarded for information to:
Secretary to the President.
Secretary to the Vice-President.
(K.L. Sharma)

Copy also forwarded for information to:
Principal Secretary to the Prime Minister.
(K.L. Sharma)

(K.L. Sharma)

(Distribution Branch)/Rajya Sabha Secretariat (Distribution Branch)/ Establishment Officer,
Department of Personnel & Training/Ministry of External Affairs (Protocol Division)/Press
Information Bureau/Section Officer, NGO Section, Prime Minister's Office.
(K.L. Shama)
